59
00:04:02.165 --> 00:04:06.303
<i>♪ Arabian nights</i>

60
00:04:06.435 --> 00:04:10.206
<i>♪ Like Arabian days</i>

61
00:04:10.339 --> 00:04:14.110
<i>♪ They seem to excite
