Hmm.
That's a lovely necklace.

73
00:05:03.792 --> 00:05:05.261
So. where does Abu come from?

74
00:05:05.361 --> 00:05:06.329
He. uh...

75
00:05:06.695 --> 00:05:07.864
Oh!

76
